 border around the picture.\', \'By default, image will align at the left side of the page, but you can use align attribute to set it in the center or right.\']','[\'\n<img src = \"Image URL\" ... attributes-list/>\n\', \'\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n\n   <head>\n      <title>Using Image in Webpage</title>\n   </head>\n	\n   <body>\n      <p>Simple Image Insert</p>\n      <img src = \"/html/images/test.png\" alt = \"Test Image\" />\n   </body>\n	\n</html>\n\', \'\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n\n   <head>\n      <title>Using Image in Webpage</title>\n   </head>\n	\n   <body>\n      <p>Simple Image Insert</p>\n      <img src = \"/html/images/test.png\" alt = \"Test Image\" />\n   </body>\n	\n</html>\n\', \'\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n\n   <head>\n      <title>Set Image Width and Height</title>\n   </head>\n	\n   <body>\n      <p>Setting image width and height</p>\n      <img src = \"/html/images/test.png\" alt = \"Test Image\" width = \"150\" height = \"100\"/>\n   </body>\n	\n</html>\n\', \'\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n\n   <head>\n      <title>Set Image Border</title>\n   </head>\n	\n   <body>\n      <p>Setting image Border</p>\n      <img src = \"/html/images/test.png\" alt = \"Test Image\" border = \"3\"/>\n   </body>\n	\n</html>\n\', \'\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n\n   <head>\n      <title>Set Image Alignment</title>\n   </head>\n	\n   <body>\n      <p>Setting image Alignment</p>\n      <img src = \"/html/images/test.png\" alt = \"Test Image\" border = \"3\" align = \"right\"/>\n   </body>\n	\n</html>\n\']','[\'\n<img src = \"Image URL\" ... attributes-list/>\n\']','[]','[]'),(10,'[\'HTML - Tables\']','[\'Example\', \'Table Heading\', \'Cellpadding and Cellspacing Attributes\', \'Colspan and Rowspan Attributes\', \'Tables Backgrounds\', \'Table Height and Width\', \'Table Caption\', \'Table Header, Body, and Footer\', \'Nested Tables\', \'Useful Video Courses\']','[\'Example\', \'Example\', \'Example\', \'Example\', \'Example\', \'Example\', \'Example\', \'Example\']','[\'h